{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/use-an-id-attribute-to-style-an-element","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-css","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi `id` atribut za stilizovanje elementa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Jedna dobra stvar kod <code>id</code> atributa je to sto ih, kao i klase, mozete stilizovati pomocu CSS-a.</p>\n<p>Ipak, <code>id</code> ne treba ponavljati i treba ga koristiti samo na jednom elementu. <code>id</code> takodje ima veci prioritet (specificity) od klase, pa ako su oba dodeljena istom elementu i imaju konfliktne stilove, primenice se stil <code>id</code>-a.</p>\n<p>Evo primera kako mozete uzeti element sa <code>id</code> atributom <code>cat-photo-element</code> i dodeliti mu zelenu pozadinu. U svom <code>style</code> elementu:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">#cat-photo-element {\n  background-color: green;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zapamtite da se u <code>style</code> elementu klase navode sa <code>.</code> ispred imena. <code>id</code> vrednosti se navode sa <code>#</code> ispred imena.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87dee1348bd9aede07836","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Pokusajte da svom form elementu, koji sada ima <code>id</code> <code>cat-photo-form</code>, dodelite zelenu boju pozadine.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cakyZfL","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18339,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/use-an-id-attribute-to-style-an-element"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n<style>\n  .red-text {\n    color: red;\n  }\n\n  h2 {\n    font-family: Lobster, monospace;\n  }\n\n  p {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-family: monospace;\n  }\n\n  .thick-green-border {\n    border-color: green;\n    border-width: 10px;\n    border-style: solid;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n\n  .smaller-image {\n    width: 100px;\n  }\n\n  .silver-background {\n    background-color: silver;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<h2 class=\"red-text\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\n<main>\n  <p class=\"red-text\">Click here to view more <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\n\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"smaller-image thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n\n  <div class=\"silver-background\">\n    <p>Things cats love:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>catnip</li>\n      <li>laser pointers</li>\n      <li>lasagna</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\n    <ol>\n      <li>flea treatment</li>\n      <li>thunder</li>\n      <li>other cats</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\" id=\"cat-photo-form\">\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label><br>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" checked> Loving</label>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Energetic</label><br>\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n  </form>\n</main>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vas <code>form</code> element treba da ima <code>id</code> <code>cat-photo-form</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector('form').getAttribute('id'), 'cat-photo-form');"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>form</code> element treba da ima zeleni <code>background-color</code>.</p>","testString":"const catPhotoForm = document.querySelector('#cat-photo-form');\nconst backgroundColor = window.getComputedStyle(catPhotoForm)['background-color'];\nassert.strictEqual(backgroundColor, 'rgb(0, 128, 0)');"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>form</code> element treba da ima <code>id</code> atribut.</p>","testString":"assert.match(__helpers.removeHtmlComments(code), /<form.*cat-photo-form.*>/gi);\nassert.lengthOf(__helpers.removeHtmlComments(code).match(/<form.*cat-photo-form.*>/gi), 1)"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da dodeljujete <code>class</code> ili <code>style</code> atribute svom <code>form</code> elementu.</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(__helpers.removeHtmlComments(code), /<form.*style.*>/gi);\nassert.notMatch(__helpers.removeHtmlComments(code), /<form.*class.*>/gi);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#basic-css","dashedName":"use-an-id-attribute-to-style-an-element","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-css","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/adjust-the-padding-of-an-element","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/set-the-id-of-an-element","id":"bad87dee1348bd9aede07836","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>@media (max-width: 350px) {:root {--penguin-size: 200px; --penguin-skin: black;}}</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/use-an-id-attribute-to-style-an-element"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}